This is the simple Raspberry pi Project for beginner
firstly make connection of PIR Sensor and Raspberry pi .
open the terminal on Raspberry pi with installed python IDLE 
and directly run the main.py file 


In the program write your own email id passward and user email id .

#Interfacing of PIR to Raspberry pi

  Pins                                            Connection With Raspberry pi
  VCC                                             Connect Any power Pin of Raspberry pi (5v)
  GND                                             Ground
  OUT                                             Connect To GPIO Pin 23 (you can connect to any GPIO Pin)
